To install this thinobject system locally or on a remote host, run bin/install.

Examples:

  $ bin/install -h
  $ bin/install --help
  # bin/install --prefix /usr/lib
  $ bin/install --prefix ~
  $ bin/install --prefix ~ --host me@some.host
  $ bin/install

The last example is the same as:

  $ bin/install --prefix /usr/local

